reviews: Great product for the price. I am more than pleased with the quality and durability. Wouldn’t consider military grade but it’s thick, lots of padding and nice extra pocket space for accessories and charger.

review_title: Quality is ok, was expecting a little more tho.
reviews: Sunglasses are decent. The lens is reflective so you won’t see your eyes. I wish they were slightly bigger and covered my eyes more. The frame does not seem very durable.

review_title: Great product that’s worth more than it’s price.
reviews: Great scale, if your feet are size 11 or more you should definitely get this model and not the smaller white one. I love the colour and back lit screen. This device takes AA batteries, if I could change anything I’d like it to be a us rechargeable model but. I’m so happy with the accuracy and general performance/quality that I couldn’t give it any less than 5 stars.
The actually writing is crisp and clean but the floral print around it is so dull and blurry. Was a total disappointment and do not recommend for anyone. Feels very cheap too
Big fan of the mint green Color. I dropped my case once and gave it a little scratch. Paying the low price for this case is worth it for sure
Couldn’t ask for more! Price is great and everything seems to be great quality
Love it! The only issue I have is I’m concerned this won’t be compatible with cases that hole the pen while it charges

review_title: Little too pricy but it’s nice
reviews: It’s a nice headband. Might cost a little more than it’s actually worth but it fits good and has a nice thick rubber elastic in the middle

From the images it looks almost like a fake leather front. It is plastic feeling but doesn’t feel that cheap. Doesn’t feel too durable either. Good for the price but if you want to protect your $1400+ iPad Pro I’d consider looking at more high end models. This case will be a good start but I’ll def upgrade down the road.
Quality seems fine. Hat is longer than pictured. You gotta do some adjusting and playing around to make it for right, otherwise it looks real goofy.
Product is nice, the chain that it comes on is cheap and looked like it will break easily. Ordered a better chain to wear with it.
Quality is good, fits smaller than expected. Normally wear Large. Had to get XL and almost snug on the legs. Hangs quite lpwnon crotch area. Feels nice and soft and is cute.

review_title: *ORDER SIZE LARGER THAN YOU USUALLY WEAR*
reviews: Quality is fine for the price paid, also arrived way earlier then estimated time.

review_title: Mediocre, but good enough for a costume.
reviews:
Stitching on the emblem was already coming off as I pulled out of package. Does not have good shape on top.

Good enough if you just want it as a gag or costume. But if you want the. Real deal or anything close to high quality, you will regret this item.
